Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SHADOW RAIMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And another!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel a little sluggish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew using Doru Aura twice in a row\Nwould take its toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was able to do it because\Nyou understood what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you planned to use\NDoru Aura twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realized that Ban used his\NKōmanotsue to survive my Doru Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that he wouldn't be able to\Nwithstand it twice in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be possible\Nif you healed my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't work if he had dodged it,\Nbut if he was using his staff to block it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if you fired a second one while\Nthe energy of the first one remained,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be two Doru Aura's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way... he survived that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all so quick\Nthe reality hasn't sunk in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was always only one Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To hit something with\NDoru Aura twice in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a destructive force\Nthat should normally be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it's Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody but Ban would be able to\Nblock a Doru Aura spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Ban is too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His strength is the reason he ended up\Nbeing hit by an attack that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess being too strong\Nisn't all it seems to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stand proud, Hero! You've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've defeated the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty big.\NIt was the biggest shock I've felt today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Either it was caused by Dai... or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We should hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We know he can't resist.\NThere's no need to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to finish him off, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too forgiving, Maam!\NHow many times have we fought this beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We should finish him here\Nor we'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm right, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Dai loses to Ban\Nit'll be meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we kill Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're infighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:06:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your teamwork sure sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Royal Guard was much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be able to move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's immortal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! Do you still want to\Nshow him mercy now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell me!\NI'm finishing him off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your useless babbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,without your permission...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have revealed this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human? No. A Darkling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The true face that even Ron Berku feared\Nis that of this slender young man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This presence... I recognize it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All this force... from just a push?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have done something truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even I can escape the severe\Npunishment from King Ban this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even execution may be unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing this face\Nis that great of a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do it without\NKing Ban's permission...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Are you trying to provoke me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about that pompous face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What overwhelming malice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not as thick as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sensed my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! I'm... I'm being\Noverwhelmed by his pressure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By... By this normal-looking...\Nordinary guy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Dark Aura was much stronger\Nwhen he had his mask on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good. Be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Babble all you want after you eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it, Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aura Knuckle!{i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym's Orichalcum arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He twisted it off! Forcefully!\NAnd so casually!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And not by using his opponent's strength\Nagainst them like I would!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He tore it off with brute strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! My arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Very impressive, Larhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal hit would have caused\Nthat arm to break or dent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,These shattered fragments of Orichalcum\Nare proof of your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You and that pawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,may be warriors of the highest level\Non this Surface World.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But you cannot hope to\Nmatch me in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the face of\Nthe strongest man in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What about Ban?! Isn't Ban\Nsupposed to be greater than you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban is a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His wisdom and Magic Power\Nare indeed unparalleled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But in terms of a powerful body,\NI am currently above him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am stronger than King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the strongest of the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}DARK AURA PUPPETRY HAND{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.48,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}AURA KNUCKLE{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There! I cast Behoma on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about the others.\NLet's hurry back to the White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong, Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, my body feels a little weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be healed more than I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not fully healed?!\NWith a Behoma spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm better than when I cast Doru Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've only recovered\Nwhat you would naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To not fully recover your stamina\Nfrom a Behoma spell is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. It could be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage from Dark Aura\Ncan't be healed with Heal-type magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be possible that\Nthe Dragonic Aura is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If the rebound from that double Doru Aura\Nhas left residual damage to you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that is unaffected by Heal-type magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already defeated Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We either let it heal naturally,\Nor wait until Heal-type magic works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is give it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you think it'll take?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban may be strong,\Nbut he can't be stronger than Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Larhart's working with the others,\Nthey'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting your power back fully comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can think about Popp,\NMaster Aban and the others after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to help in that state\Nyou'll only drag them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so blunt, Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's\Nwhat makes you reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What kind of compliment is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still feel a trembling in my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still have...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this terrible feeling...\Nthat something bad is going to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stronger than Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying you're\Nthe real big boss of the Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That you're above Ban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With your meager intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't understand even if I\Nexplained my relationship with King Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll answer your first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... you're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He could... actually be stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That power is beyond human comprehension!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It could be greater than Ban's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful as you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You could live for centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and never have the chance\Nto be killed by one like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This gift of death is far beyond\Nwhat you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing will work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But we won't go down so easily!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may seem that\Nwe're powerless against him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but if we can slow him down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We still have our last option!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Medoroa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel an abnormal amount\Nof expectation on my shoulders!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about pressure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I use it head on, he might reflect it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he ain't slow either!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to cast it at the perfect time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heal me so I can fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get him in a hold somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I do,\Njust cast that big spell of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-I couldn't do...\N-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?!\NHe'll kill every one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You still seem ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bravery is commendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even against such overwhelming power\Nnone of you have lost hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You did manage\Nto fight King Ban once after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for your finishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a metallic life form,\Nbut I can't sacrifice you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hesitate like that and you'll end up dead\Nwith that girl you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If my life is all it costs,\Nconsider it a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does a random enemy like you\Nknow about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buddy, talk about obvious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop squabbling and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what they're planning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I guess I'll join in on that gamble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes! It's round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone but us, keep your distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick to ranged attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Larhart and Hym's\Nsimultaneous attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...aren't hitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not that they aren't hitting!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like before,\Nsome attacks are hitting home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I can't even hold him in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My Beast King Indomitable Blast\Nisn't even slowing him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you okay?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to be saved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I could move freely!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's too strong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate to disappoint everyone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but there's no time\Nto ready a Medoroa spell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a clean face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always had a thing\Nfor handsome guys, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been hit numerous times\Neven when he had his mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I even hit him in the face\Nwith my Refractor Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet he doesn't have a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, right now I'm Mr. Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit him in the face\Nwith your Refractor Fist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I've uncovered\Nthe secret of his immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal and indestructible\Nare two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban may be powerful\Nand seemingly immune to damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Refractor Fist\Novercharges biological functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, he should retain\Nsome sort of mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His body isn't alive.\NIt has no biological functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I will give you a chance\Nto cast Medoroa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait! That's crazy!\N-Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as you know,\NI suffer from Glossy Ankleitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight for long,\Nso make good use of that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wasn't Brokin's illness something else?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget about that!\NI don't have time to think about that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now a clown is going to buy time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret of your immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the Secret Spell of Frozen Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know of the Secret Spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:26.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brokin realizes the secret\Nbehind the unmasked Mystban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As he confuses Mystban\Nwith his flexible movements,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp looks for a window to cast Medoroa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is Mystban's secret\Nthat Brokin explains?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And can Popp achieve victory\Nwith his Medoroa Spell?{\i0}
